comments: Williams (BOS) and Davis (LAL) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs prior to the screen being set.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Tatum's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kornet (BOS) legally contests Davis's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Williams (BOS) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with James (LAL), which affects James's (LAL) SQBR.
Williams (BOS) briefly bring both hands to Davis (LAL) and marginal contact occurs as Davis sets the pick.
Williams (BOS) legally contests James's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
James (LAL) does not overtly or abruptly extend his leg out as incidental contact occurs with Williams (BOS) during the jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) and Davis (LAL) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) firms up in Tatum's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the dribble hand-off.
Kornet (BOS) initiates contact with Davis's (LAL) arm, which affects his alley-hoop attempt.
James (LAL) brings his arm toward Tatum's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs during Tatum's (BOS) drive.
Davis (LAL) briefly brings his arm forward to Tatum (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as he sets the pick.
Williams (BOS) briefly bring both hands to Davis (LAL) and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Williams (BOS) initiates contact with Davis (LAL) that affects his FOM as the pick is set.
Williams (BOS) firms up in Westbrook's (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as the off-ball screen is set.
Reaves (LAL) avoids making contact and legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) engages with Brown Jr. (LAL) and marginal contact occurs as Tatum (BOS) releases away to retrieve the inbound pass.
Westbrook (LAL) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Brown (BOS) during his jump shot attempt.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Brown (BOS) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes one step before releasing the pass.
James (LAL) initiates foot to foot contact with Brown (BOS) which affects his SBQR at the start of his drive.
Brown Jr. (LAL) commits a take foul on Brown (BOS).
Davis (LAL) is absorbing the initial contact that occurs with Smart (BOS) and incidental contact occurs as Smart (BOS) attempts to move over the screen.
